  "body": "Support for setting [NO_NEW_PRIVS](https://www.kernel.org/doc/Documentation/prctl/no_new_privs.txt) was added in docker 1.11 (https://github.com/docker/docker/issues/20329). This feature will be much more useful once user namespace support is added (https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/pull/34569), but I believe it is also relevant when paired with seccomp or LSM (SELinux or AppArmor).\r\n\r\n/cc @mrunalp @kubernetes/sig-node ",
